name: Printing Head V2
description:
The Printing Head V2 is capable of printing PLA, PETG, ABS, NYLON, HIPS, PC up to 250°C. It features a full metal replaceable nozzle and 40W heating cartridge for better performances, as well as a secondary cooling fan.
The design is clog-proof and In addition can be fully disassembled and cleaned when necessary.
